(Inspired by Sinatra, it does not follow the model�view�controller pattern used in other frameworks, such as Spring MVC,1)
(Instead, Spark is intended for quickly creating web-applications in Java with minimal effort,1)
(It is an alternative to other Java web application frameworks such as JAX-RS, Play framework and Spring MVC,1)
(It is to be used in the Spark word count program,2)
(It runs on an embedded Jetty web server by default, but can be configured to run on other webservers,1)
